RL10B-2燃烧室的一处焊接裂缝被查证时导致运送猎户座-3通信卫星的德尔塔三型运载火箭失败的元凶。<ref>{{cite web | title = Delta 269 (Delta III) Investigation Report | url = http://www.boeing.com/defense-space/space/delta/delta3/d3_report.pdf | publisher = [[Boeing|Boeing]] | format = PDF | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20010616012841/http://www.boeing.com/defense-space/space/delta/delta3/d3_report.pdf | archivedate = 2001-06-16 | accessdate = 2009-07-20 }}</ref>

另一个改进版本是RL10A-4-2，用于[[宇宙神五号|宇宙神五号]]的上面级。

